data.description:
THE SELLER HAS AN ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE! Balance $719k @ 2.49%  This exquisite residence nestled in Parker, Colorado.
Situated in a serene and highly sought-after neighborhood, this home boasts a prime location with convenient access to amenities, schools, parks, and major transportation routes. The surrounding area features well-manicured landscapes and welcoming ambiance, perfect for a peaceful yet vibrant lifestyle.

The exterior of the residence showcases a contemporary architectural design, complemented by a pleasing color palette and meticulous craftsmanship. The curb appeal is enhanced by a well-maintained lawn, mature trees, and a welcoming front entrance.

Upon entering the residence, you are greeted by an open and inviting floor plan that seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The interior is adorned with high-quality finishes, including hardwood flooring, elegant fixtures, and large windows that fill the space with natural light. The spacious living room is perfect for gatherings & relaxation, while the gourmet kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances, ample counter space, and a center island, making it a chef's delight.

The residence offers multiple bedrooms, including a lavish master suite that provides a tranquil retreat with its ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet, and private balcony. Each bedroom is thoughtfully designed, offering comfort and privacy for all family members and guests.

Additional amenities of this exceptional home include a dedicated home office, a well-equipped gym, and a generous outdoor living space, featuring a patio and a landscaped backyard. This outdoor oasis provides a perfect setting for entertaining, alfresco dining, or simply enjoying the beauty of Colorado's scenery.

12961 Bridge View Lane is more than a residence; it is a sanctuary of sophistication and comfort, designed to meet the demands of a discerning homeowner seeking the epitome of modern living in a picturesque Colorado setting.
